{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044520/extras/EN_Headline.png?t=1737819749\" />Sit back and run your own coffee shop in the caffeine-filled world of Coffee Express! Coffee Express is a single-player first-person simulation game where you take over your coffee shop as a barista and work your way up to becoming the town's favorite coffee shop.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044520/extras/RealisticCoffeeExpreince.png?t=1737819749\" />Coffee Express is no ordinary coffee making game. All types of coffee have realistic brewing stages. So you may need to use several different items to make a coffee. Espresso and filter coffee makers, portafilters and more will become yours as you develop your shop!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044520/extras/ShowYourSkills.png?t=1737819749\" />Sometimes you may want to go out of the routine or the customer may ask you to do something different. For example, a cute customer might ask you to draw a flower on their latte or write something silly on their coffee cup. Maybe you need to go outside the recipe? We leave some things up to your talent for a freer experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044520/extras/Townspeople.png?t=1737819749\" />Walk around the street and visit other shops. Listen to the interesting stories of the customers and treat them the way you like.  Be a good barista, a good neighbor and a good friend &lt;3 (Or not to be...) Remember there is no stress in this game, only coffee and peace!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Coffee of Day!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3044520/290fe5d4fb85903ce54fab5bfc918abb6811c8c7.jpg"},{"name":"Shopping List is Complete!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3044520/38f73db1a321fe22eb8ccee81f6f6b1f93f540aa.jpg"},{"name":"It's So Clean!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3044520/1c95b55645ce1b9b49bd4f48d700a0f0729d0df1.jpg"},{"name":"Latte Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3044520/929c59b0b304f2866bf8fed25f15b1b1b53df1f3.jpg"},{"name":"Business is Growing!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3044520/52f50049909a4ba9fb6a344e0e9f0f876b94b227.jpg"}],"total":5},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044520/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737819749","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044520/page.bg.jpg?t=1737819749","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044520/bee4305df54ff4ec0d0efc9632d7c500d404253e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737819749","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044520/bee4305df54ff4ec0d0efc9632d7c500d404253e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737819749","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044520/extras/EN_Headline.png?t=1737819749\" />Sit back and run your own coffee shop in the caffeine-filled world of Coffee Express! Coffee Express is a single-player first-person simulation game where you take over your coffee shop as a barista and work your way up to becoming the town'